# Production builds only — Vite loads `.env.production` when you run `vite build`
# (including `make deploy` / `pnpm run deploy`). It is not loaded by `vite dev`.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.production` in this directory and set your deployed
# worker-api origin (no trailing slash). Keep `.env.production` out of git if
# the URL is private, or commit a non-secret default for your team.
#
# From repo root without cd:
#   pnpm turbo run deploy --filter=front-app
